text: Rose of Washington Square is a 1939 American musical drama movie directed by Gregory Ratoff and stars Tyrone Power, Alice Faye, Al Jolson, Moroni Olsen, Winifred Harris, Joyce Compton, William Frawley, Ralph Dunn, Louis Prima. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1939 drama movies Category:1930s American musical movies Category:1930s American drama movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Gregory Ratoff
